Question: At least one chew toy is laying near a chow dog in one image.

Reference Answer: True

Left image URL: http://www.chow-dalen.ru/dogs/arven/arven5.jpg

Right image URL: https://i.ytimg.com/vi/B1Q1x-1V81k/maxresdefault.jpg

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is there a chow dog in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is there a chow dog in the image?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is there a chew toy laying near the chow dog?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is there a chew toy laying near the chow dog?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER2}')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} and {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} xor {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
